      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It’s just a short walk from their house to the park, we find Lizzy’s On The Green - a cute little coffee and pastry shop right in a park that is bustling with people. While waiting for the coffee Dave suggests we head over the to the little cheese shop to grab something for breakfast.",
            "link": null
          },
