    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We’re heading to the Borough Market on the Thames in central London. The cycle takes us about forty minutes through the backroads and Molly and Dave entertain us with facts about the city. The cars are very considerate of cyclists and I find it an absolutely amazing experience. We drops the bikes and then walk over the bridge across the Thames to the market. ",
            "link": null
          },
