          "text": {
            "content": "Upon arriving home the three take their positions in bed and I jump onto Dave’s bike to meet my friend Benji. We cycle to Clissold Park where Benji whips out a blanket and we drink some tea and have a really beautiful catchup on all aspects of life. ",
