    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Today is a busy day. Dave messages me and we’re heading out for dinner. Benji and I cycle back and I immediately get ready to walk to dinner. Dave and Molly talk about how House of MoMo - our dinner destination - has delicious dumplings but usually an enormous queue. Our expectations are set yet we’re surprised when there is no queue and a table for four waiting. The dumplings live up the the hype.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
