      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We’re feeling full and have some time to kill before our movie so we walk some laps through the cold streets of Saturday night London. Scenes of every possible situation play out before us and we walk through them as if detached somehow. We grab a snack for the movie and then it’s time to go to the RIO cinema.",
